{"id":14327,"date":"2024-02-09T17:24:44","date_gmt":"2020-09-09T11:54:44","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=14327"},"modified":"2023-08-17T14:35:50","modified_gmt":"2023-08-17T09:05:50","slug":"sectional-sofa-design-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/sectional-sofa-design-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"Sectional Sofa Design Ideas For Your Home!"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Sectional Sofas have become the most popular style of sofas lately. But which design will suit your living room the best? Here\u2019s a lowdown on some of our favourite sectional sofa design ideas to help you make an informed choice!<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>When it&#8217;s about must-have furniture pieces in your home, a sofa is the most important one! It anchors the look of your living room. A sofa it&#8217;s where you read, chill, watch shows with your family and entertain your guests. And because a sofa performs so many duties the idea of picking the right one for a good amount of time can be challenging. You&#8217;ll need a sofa design that&#8217;s functional and blends beautifully with the overall design style of your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">home interiors<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you fancy a stylish sofa that is also packed with comfort and functionality, a sectional sofa is a perfect option for you. A sectional sofa can be easily configured to match the layout of your living room and style.&nbsp; To help you make the right choice from the different sectional sofa designs available for you to choose from we bring you a lowdown on various sectional sofa designs.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let&#8217;s start!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Full-length Leather Sectional Sofa Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A full-length leather sectional sofa is perfect if you have a big family with kids and there&#8217;s always someone to spill food and drinks! Leather sofas are extremely easy to clean, and since it&#8217;s a sectional sofa, it&#8217;s big enough to accommodate everyone!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Leather sectional sofas are the most popular sectional sofa designs, especially for big fat Indian families where style and functionality go hand in hand! These sofa designs are readily available in different colours and textures to match the overall aesthetics of your living room.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09165326\/full-length-leather-large-sectional-sofas.jpg\" alt=\"Full-length large sectional sofas in brown leather are perfect for a big family &amp; aesthetics of your living room.\" class=\"wp-image-14329\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09165326\/full-length-leather-large-sectional-sofas.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09165326\/full-length-leather-large-sectional-sofas-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09165326\/full-length-leather-large-sectional-sofas-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09165326\/full-length-leather-large-sectional-sofas-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Luxury Sectional Sofa Design With Velvet Upholstery<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Velvet has royal charm to it. Use it on your furniture in your home and it becomes a luxurious corner in a snap! Here, a teal velvet sectional sofa adds a much-needed pop of colour and a touch of luxury. Further, a velvet upholstered sofa in a deep shade doesn&#8217;t show stains much and can be cleaned with a quick vacuum.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09165521\/luxury-sectional-sofa-design.jpg\" alt=\"Luxury sectional furniture with velvet upholstery adds a much-needed pop of colour and a touch of luxury.\" class=\"wp-image-14331\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09165521\/luxury-sectional-sofa-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09165521\/luxury-sectional-sofa-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09165521\/luxury-sectional-sofa-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09165521\/luxury-sectional-sofa-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Upgrade your living space with hassle-free interior design\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/16184519\/upgrade-your-living-space-with-hassle-free-interior-design.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Small Sectional Sofa For A Small Room<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you like the idea of having a sectional sofa but you feel it won&#8217;t fit in your small living room this might just solve your problem! A small sectional sofa design like this can fit even the smallest living room. It works great for a small family or just you and your partner, a 1BHK or a studio apartment. Not to mention the colour, texture and patterns of your sofa can be customised to your taste and preference.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09165808\/small-room-sectional-sofa.jpg\" alt=\"Small room sectional sofa in white coloured with pillows works great for a small family.\" class=\"wp-image-14334\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09165808\/small-room-sectional-sofa.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09165808\/small-room-sectional-sofa-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09165808\/small-room-sectional-sofa-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09165808\/small-room-sectional-sofa-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">U Shaped Sectional Sofa Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A U-shaped sectional sofa design is ideal if you have a big family, if you entertain often or if you have a living room that extends into a dining area. A U-shaped sectional sofa like this will help separate your dining area from the living room as it covers a significant area and creates an opening because of its shape. Like all the other sectional sofa designs, this design is also available in different colours and textures for you to pick your favourite as per your taste and the existing colour scheme and aesthetics of your living room.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09165859\/u-shaped-best-sectional-couches.jpg\" alt=\"U-shaped designer sectional sofas in white coloured add aesthetics of your living room.\" class=\"wp-image-14335\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09165859\/u-shaped-best-sectional-couches.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09165859\/u-shaped-best-sectional-couches-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09165859\/u-shaped-best-sectional-couches-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09165859\/u-shaped-best-sectional-couches-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Low Height Sectional Sofa With Tufted Seats<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A sectional sofa with a touch of chesterfield sofa&#8217;s tufted seats is everything chic that your living room deserves! Further, this sectional sofa design is low in height that makes it unique and offers a perfect height to straighten your legs and helps you maintain the right sitting posture. The tufted seats do not only make this otherwise plain sofa look extremely stylish but are also great as a backrest.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09165415\/low-height-sectional-sofa-with-tufted-seats.jpg\" alt=\"Low height sectional sofa with tufted seats look incredibly stylish but also fabulous as a backrest.\" class=\"wp-image-14330\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09165415\/low-height-sectional-sofa-with-tufted-seats.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09165415\/low-height-sectional-sofa-with-tufted-seats-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09165415\/low-height-sectional-sofa-with-tufted-seats-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09165415\/low-height-sectional-sofa-with-tufted-seats-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sectional Sofa With Patterned Upholstered Seating<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are bored with the conventional plain sofa styles and would like to add a sofa that&#8217;s stylish and unique, we suggest you choose a sofa with patterned seating like this one. A patterned sofa will add a touch of freshness in your living room. There are several patterns and textures available in the market for you to choose from. You can also pick a dual-layered sofa as shown in this image where the base of the sofa is in solid grey and topped with a patterned seating that creates a cohesive look.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09165614\/sectional-sofa-design-ideas-with-patterned-upholstered.jpg\" alt=\"Patterned upholstered seating is the best sectional couches and adds a touch of freshness in this white living room.\" class=\"wp-image-14332\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09165614\/sectional-sofa-design-ideas-with-patterned-upholstered.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09165614\/sectional-sofa-design-ideas-with-patterned-upholstered-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09165614\/sectional-sofa-design-ideas-with-patterned-upholstered-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09165614\/sectional-sofa-design-ideas-with-patterned-upholstered-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Want a living room that oozes luxury\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/09112033\/want-a-living-room-that-oozes-luxury.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Wide Sectional Sofa Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>By now you know that sectional sofas are elongated and are usually long and form a U or L shape. Here is a compact sofa that&#8217;s wide enough to accommodate your tiny family and binge watch your favourite shows together. This sofa further doubles up as a sofa bed for the unexpected guests who are in for a sleepover!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09170000\/wide-designer-sectional-sofas.jpg\" alt=\"A wide compact sofa in green is perfect for tiny family &amp; doubles up as a sofa bed are sectional sofa design ideas.\" class=\"wp-image-14336\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09170000\/wide-designer-sectional-sofas.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09170000\/wide-designer-sectional-sofas-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09170000\/wide-designer-sectional-sofas-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09170000\/wide-designer-sectional-sofas-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And that&#8217;s all for today! We hope that this helps you to pick the right sectional sofa design for your home. Don&#8217;t forget to add a lot of cushions to make it a lot more cosy and perfect for family time!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Explore, More About<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/15-sofa-designs-for-modern-living-room\/\">15 Sofa Designs For Modern Living Room<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/different-sofa-styles-for-your-home\/\">Different Sofa Styles For Your Home<\/a><\/li><\/ul>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Functional Interior Designs?<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with smart solutions<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- 